cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with point cloud classification using a fully convolutional neural network. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The application of the proposed method to airborne LiDAR systems suggests that it could also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
